{"tid":547026,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"流感再多4人死亡","createTime":"2018-02-01T04:55:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-01T06:10:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40f40d2a478732d914fb858cb1f49e11876d4297","tid":547026,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T04:55:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180201/20291985\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F20291985&d=tKULNKj27C%2FG92dllZ2ZRJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d02fedeb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180201%2F20291985&h=9067544e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180201/20291985</a><br />\n<br />\n流感再多4人死亡<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180201/large/01la6p3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180201%2Flarge%2F01la6p3.jpg&h=5c50837b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本港在未來一周持續寒冷，流感病毒在寒冷天氣下更加活躍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】本港在未來一周持續寒冷，流感病毒在寒冷天氣下更加活躍，家庭醫生林永和指，預期因流感求診的病人會增加，近日其診所每日約有20個病人經快速測試確診流感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n增1宗兒童嚴重感染個案<br />\n<br />\n此外，他稱接到藥廠通知，最快下周三會有新一批流感疫苗送抵。林永和補充，流感與傷風病徵有差別，流感常有發燒、周身骨痛，且發病快；傷風病人則常有鼻水，一般只輕微發燒或無發燒。<br />\n<br />\n天文台預測今日市區最低氣溫僅7℃，新界再低兩三度，最凍的打鼓嶺早上只有3℃；隨後數天市區最低氣溫料徘徊於7至10℃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180201/large/a0704a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180201%2Flarge%2Fa0704a.gif&h=1f8e11ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心表示，前日本港新增7宗成人嚴重流感個案，4人死亡，今年累積161宗成人個案，87人死亡。兒童嚴重個案昨日新增1宗，累積增至11宗，2人死亡。新增個案為15歲女童，上月22日出現發燒及咳嗽帶痰等病徵，前日入住聯合醫院並轉往兒科深切治療部留醫。她無打流感針，臨床診斷為乙流併發敗血性休克，現情況穩定。此外，過去24小時有9名58至91歲病人因低溫而送往急症室，當中3人危殆、3人嚴重，另外3人情況穩定。<br />\n<br />\n■記者袁樂婷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180201/large/a0704b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180201%2Flarge%2Fa0704b.gif&h=9101160c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8f74a112ae83cb39337ef8ed539b89221fd5fbba","tid":547026,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:09:37.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"7badc6b92c5ca10aa5ee52d79efaf299b8728b32","tid":547026,"uid":123711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}